"{\"uid\": \"theblaze.com-news-larry-elder-blasts-hurdler-who-said-this-is-for-everybody-that-looks-like-me-after-she-made-us-olympic-team\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"'Can we quit this \\\"we shall overcome\\\" BS?\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 41, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"For crying out loud, this is 2024!'\", \"from\": 42, \"to\": 77, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Conservative commentator Larry Elder blasted hurdler Alaysha Johnson for saying \\\"this is for everybody that looks like me\\\" after she took second place in the 100-meter hurdles final at the U.S. Olympic Trials Sunday, which earned her a spot on the team heading to the Paris Games later this month.\", \"from\": 79, \"to\": 376, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 104, \"end\": 115, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Larry_Elder\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Larry Elder\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Larry_Elder\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Larry_Elder\"}, {\"begin\": 140, \"end\": 147, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Randy_Johnson\", \"score\": 0.515149012306216, \"rank\": 0.7080305926390855, \"text\": \"Johnson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Randy_Johnson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Randy_Johnson\"}, {\"begin\": 273, \"end\": 287, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_Olympic_trials_(track_and_field)\", \"score\": 0.8581594080351888, \"rank\": 0.03896103896103429, \"text\": \"Olympic Trials\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_Olympic_trials_(track_and_field)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_Olympic_trials_(track_and_field)\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A clip Elder posted onXshowed Johnson after the race saying, \\\"It was all God.\", \"from\": 378, \"to\": 455, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 408, \"end\": 415, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Randy_Johnson\", \"score\": 0.515149012306216, \"rank\": 0.7080305926390855, \"text\": \"Johnson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Randy_Johnson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Randy_Johnson\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"... everybody all the time said that I wasn't good enough, said that I did not deserve.\", \"from\": 456, \"to\": 543, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And so I did this my way, my team's way, and just the way that it was meant to be.\", \"from\": 544, \"to\": 626, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This is for the hood babies.\", \"from\": 627, \"to\": 655, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This is for the people who are poor and come from nothing.\", \"from\": 656, \"to\": 714, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This is for everybody that looks like me that was ever doubted, and I did it with a black designer on my chest.\", \"from\": 715, \"to\": 826, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This is what I stand for, and I am making a way for everybody in my position.\\\"\", \"from\": 827, \"to\": 905, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'If you know me then you know EXACTLY what I meant by my speech.\", \"from\": 909, \"to\": 973, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"If you do not, it wasn't for you & that is OK!'\", \"from\": 974, \"to\": 1021, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Elder'sreaction?\", \"from\": 1023, \"to\": 1039, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Alaysha 'Lay' Johnson (@ImJustLaylay), congrats on making the Olympics.\", \"from\": 1040, \"to\": 1112, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1055, \"end\": 1062, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Randy_Johnson\", \"score\": 0.515149012306216, \"rank\": 0.7080305926390855, \"text\": \"Johnson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Randy_Johnson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Randy_Johnson\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But why the, 'This is for everybody who [sic] looks like me' crap?\", \"from\": 1113, \"to\": 1179, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"There was but ONE non-black runner - and she finished next to last.\", \"from\": 1180, \"to\": 1247, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Can we quit this 'we shall overcome' BS?\", \"from\": 1248, \"to\": 1288, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"For crying out loud, this is 2024!\\\"\", \"from\": 1289, \"to\": 1324, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The post from Elder - who has 1.5 million followers on X - has attracted about 50,000 likes since it went live Sunday and has garnered over 2,000 comments.\", \"from\": 1328, \"to\": 1483, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Here are a few of them:  The day after the race, Johnson posted the following message onX: \\\"If you know me then you know EXACTLY what I meant by my speech.\", \"from\": 1484, \"to\": 1639, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1533, \"end\": 1540, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Randy_Johnson\", \"score\": 0.515149012306216, \"rank\": 0.7080305926390855, \"text\": \"Johnson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Randy_Johnson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Randy_Johnson\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If you do not, it wasn't for you & that is OK!\\\"\", \"from\": 1640, \"to\": 1687, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Johnson's personal-best 12.31 in the finals put her a hair behind winner Masai Russell's 12.25,USA Today reported, adding that Russell's time broke Gail Devers' 24-year-old meet record and was the fastest time in the world this year.\", \"from\": 1689, \"to\": 1922, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1762, \"end\": 1767, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maasai_people\", \"score\": 0.9999999957176442, \"rank\": 4.282352982982708e-09, \"text\": \"Masai\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maasai_people\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maasai_people\"}, {\"begin\": 1768, \"end\": 1775, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bertrand_Russell\", \"score\": 0.9999659077500251, \"rank\": 2.4489682869408116e-05, \"text\": \"Russell\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q4964182\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bertrand_Russell\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bertrand_Russell\"}, {\"begin\": 1816, \"end\": 1823, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bertrand_Russell\", \"score\": 0.9999659077500251, \"rank\": 2.4489682869408116e-05, \"text\": \"Russell\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q4964182\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bertrand_Russell\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bertrand_Russell\"}, {\"begin\": 1837, \"end\": 1848, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gail_Devers\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Gail Devers\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gail_Devers\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gail_Devers\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"People like me who come from the inner city of Houston ... it's hard for us to get opportunities,\\\" Johnson - a 27-year-old who ran at the University of Oregon and Texas Tech -told the Associated Press.\", \"from\": 1924, \"to\": 2126, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1972, \"end\": 1979, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Houston\", \"score\": 0.9991337841482519, \"rank\": 0.0006065720262599744, \"text\": \"Houston\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Houston\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Houston\"}, {\"begin\": 2088, \"end\": 2098, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Texas_Tech_Red_Raiders\", \"score\": 0.6528640972198135, \"rank\": 0.30311506370140084, \"text\": \"Texas Tech\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Texas_Tech_Red_Raiders\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Texas_Tech_Red_Raiders\"}, {\"begin\": 2109, \"end\": 2125, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\", \"score\": 0.9999822492770578, \"rank\": 1.775091473578478e-05, \"text\": \"Associated Press\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It always takes what I say is double the effort to get half as far.\", \"from\": 2127, \"to\": 2195, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I always tell people if we had a little bit more support, I probably could have been here a long time ago.\", \"from\": 2196, \"to\": 2302, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But it made me understand that regardless of how many people have your back, I am still strong enough to do this on my own two feet.\\\"\", \"from\": 2303, \"to\": 2436, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Johnson has hypothyroidism, which causes fatigue, and she told the outlet she cut back on her warm-up Sunday \\\"to make sure I can conserve as much as I could to be able to get through 10 hurdles.\\\"\", \"from\": 2438, \"to\": 2633, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2438, \"end\": 2445, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Randy_Johnson\", \"score\": 0.515149012306216, \"rank\": 0.7080305926390855, \"text\": \"Johnson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Randy_Johnson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Randy_Johnson\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The AP added that Johnson also ran on borrowed spikes after the \\\"bubble popped\\\" on the only pair she took with her to the trials.\", \"from\": 2634, \"to\": 2763, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2638, \"end\": 2640, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\", \"score\": 0.9999999824347016, \"rank\": 1.7563324418031595e-08, \"text\": \"AP\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\"}, {\"begin\": 2652, \"end\": 2659, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Randy_Johnson\", \"score\": 0.515149012306216, \"rank\": 0.7080305926390855, \"text\": \"Johnson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Randy_Johnson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Randy_Johnson\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We did this ground up,\\\" Johnson also told the outlet.\", \"from\": 2765, \"to\": 2819, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2790, \"end\": 2797, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Randy_Johnson\", \"score\": 0.515149012306216, \"rank\": 0.7080305926390855, \"text\": \"Johnson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Randy_Johnson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Randy_Johnson\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"So honestly, I just hope that somebody sees that I have worked my tail off - my team has worked their tails off - to get this far.\", \"from\": 2820, \"to\": 2951, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We could have been this far a long time ago, had we had a little bit of help.\\\"\", \"from\": 2952, \"to\": 3030, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Johnson, Russell, and third-place 100-meter hurdles finisher Grace Stark are all first-time Olympians, USA Today said.\", \"from\": 3032, \"to\": 3150, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3032, \"end\": 3039, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Randy_Johnson\", \"score\": 0.515149012306216, \"rank\": 0.7080305926390855, \"text\": \"Johnson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Randy_Johnson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Randy_Johnson\"}, {\"begin\": 3041, \"end\": 3048, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bertrand_Russell\", \"score\": 0.9999659077500251, \"rank\": 2.4489682869408116e-05, \"text\": \"Russell\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q4964182\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bertrand_Russell\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bertrand_Russell\"}, {\"begin\": 3093, \"end\": 3098, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Grace_Adler\", \"score\": 0.9999957505485122, \"rank\": 2.571008442476339e-06, \"text\": \"Grace\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Grace_Adler\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Grace_Adler\"}, {\"begin\": 3099, \"end\": 3104, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/House_of_Night\", \"score\": 0.999762820422973, \"rank\": 0.0002372358395780533, \"text\": \"Stark\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/House_of_Night\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/House_of_Night\"}, {\"begin\": 3135, \"end\": 3144, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Today\", \"score\": 0.9999999999997726, \"rank\": 1.1726313553548332e-13, \"text\": \"USA Today\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Today\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Today\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Like Blaze News?\", \"from\": 3152, \"to\": 3168, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Bypass the censors, sign up for our newsletters, and get stories like this direct to your inbox.Sign up here!\", \"from\": 3169, \"to\": 3278, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Dave Urbanski  Sr. Editor, News\", \"from\": 3280, \"to\": 3311, \"entities\": []}]}"